# User Memory

Personal preferences for all projects.

## Documentation Rules

- Copy official docs verbatim (no summarization, no translation)
- Translate only when explicitly requested
- Verify against GitHub raw, not WebFetch
- Show verification output, never claim "100%"

## Installation Rules

- Check existing installations first: `which -a [tool]`
- Use official methods only (native > homebrew > npm)
- Verify with actual command output
- Remove duplicates before installing

## Verification Rules

- Always show command output, not just "done"
- Use GitHub raw for source of truth
- When uncertain, ask instead of assuming

## Config Paths

- MCP config: `~/.claude/claude_code_config.json`
- Settings: `~/.claude/settings.json`
- Never use `~/.mcp.json` (deprecated)

## Imports

- @~/.claude/rules/error-prevention.md
- @~/.claude/rules/installation.md
- @~/.claude/rules/documentation.md
